spec_data.Name: perl-HTML-TreeBuilder-LibXML
spec_data.Description:
HTML::TreeBuilder::XPath is a libxml based compatible interface to
HTML::TreeBuilder, which could be slow for a large document.
HTML::TreeBuilder::LibXML is drop-in-replacement for HTML::TreeBuilder::XPath.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 12:19:02 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: HTML::TreeBuilder and XPath compatible interface with libxml
